00:11:23.330 --> 00:11:25.330
that I was being born.

274
00:11:25.330 --> 00:11:27.330
It was the realization

275
00:11:27.330 --> 00:11:29.330
that I had come very close to dying --

276
00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:32.330
in the same way that the Earth, our mother,

277
00:11:32.330 --> 00:11:35.330
is barely holding on,

278
00:11:35.330 --> 00:11:39.330
in the same way that 75 percent of the planet

279
00:11:39.330 --> 00:11:42.330
are hardly scraping by,

280
00:11:42.330 --> 00:11:44.330
in the same way

281
00:11:44.330 --> 00:11:47.330
that there is a recipe for survival.

282
00:11:47.330 --> 00:11:49.330
What I learned

283
00:11:49.330 --> 00:11:52.330
is it has to do with attention and resources

284
00:11:52.330 --> 00:11:54.330
that everybody deserves.

285
00:11:54.330 --> 00:11:56.330
It was advocating friends

286
00:11:56.330 --> 00:11:58.330
and a doting sister.

287
00:11:58.330 --> 00:12:00.330
It was wise doctors and advanced medicine

288
00:12:00.330 --> 00:12:03.330
and surgeons who knew what to do with their hands.

289
00:12:03.330 --> 00:12:07.330
It was underpaid and really loving nurses.

290
00:12:07.330 --> 00:12:10.330
It was magic healers and aromatic oils.

291
00:12:10.330 --> 00:12:12.330
It was people who came with spells and rituals.

292
00:12:12.330 --> 00:12:15.330
It was having a vision of the future

293
00:12:15.330 --> 00:12:17.330
and something to fight for,

294
00:12:17.330 --> 00:12:20.330
because I know this struggle isn't my own.

295
00:12:20.330 --> 00:12:22.330
It was a million prayers.

296
00:12:22.330 --> 00:12:24.330
It was a thousand hallelujahs

297
00:12:24.330 --> 00:12:26.330
and a million oms.

298
00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:28.330
It was a lot of anger,

299
00:12:28.330 --> 00:12:30.330
insane humor,

300
00:12:30.330 --> 00:12:32.330
a lot of attention, outrage.

301
00:12:32.330 --> 00:12:35.330
It was energy, love and joy.

302
00:12:35.330 --> 00:12:37.330
It was all these things.

303
00:12:37.330 --> 00:12:39.330
It was all these things.

304
00:12:39.330 --> 00:12:41.330
It was all these things

305
00:12:41.330 --> 00:12:44.330
in the water, in the world, in my body.

306
00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:52.330
